title: Year 2 begins
subtitle: A new year
on-arrival: {!
Q.economic_growth -= 2;
!}
tags: event
view-if: year = 1929 and month = 1
priority: 2
max-visits: 1

A new year begins. The economy shows signs of slowing.

This event demonstrates **priority: 2** (higher priority events are shown first) and **year-based triggers**. The on-arrival block uses JavaScript to adjust variables.
